text: Agdistis asthenes is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Mongolia. The wingspan is about 20 mm. The forewings are bright grey and the hindwings are grey.Die palaearktischen Agdistis -Arten (Lepidoptera, Pterophoridae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths described in 1970
